title: OCE's largest Discord server will help you find a team and/or duo partners!

embed.description: Step up your game with a modern voice & text chat app. Crystal clear voice, multiple server and channel support, mobile apps, and more. Get your free server now!

body:
Oce's largest discord server with over 2,000 oceanic league of legends players will be a great asset for those looking for duo partners or perhaps even a team!

The server also has RP giveaways and much more.

Feel free to join it at any time! :)

replies.body: Yes, you're allowed to be a meanie weenie on this server, boo hoo :(
Please note that this guy spammed chat, didn't listen to mods, and kept on spamming, causing him to get muted.
